    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. Grid convergence (GCI < 2.1%) and output comparison (MAE 8.3%, all points within 15%) demonstrate sufficient model credibility for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions. RH < 1 criterion satisfied across all 5 operating points. The credibility evidence package supports regulatory submission for the Class II CPB device.",
